sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Service as odh-dashboard Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 1: User Authentication & Dashboard Access
    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 Request<br/>No Auth
    Router->>Service: HTTPS/8443 Reencrypt<br/>Service Serving Cert
    Service->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS Cert
    Proxy->>OAuth: Validate Session<br/>OAuth Client Secret
    OAuth-->>Proxy: User Info & Token
    Proxy->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token (Header)
    Dashboard-->>Proxy: Frontend SPA (index.html)
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS Response<br/>Set Cookie

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 2: API Request (e.g., Create Notebook)
    User->>Proxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token (Cookie)
    Proxy->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token (Header)
    Dashboard->>K8s: POST Notebook CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Dashboard: Notebook CR Created
    Dashboard->>K8s: POST ConfigMaps<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Dashboard: ConfigMap Created
    Dashboard-->>Proxy: HTTP 201 Created
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS Response<br/>Notebook Details

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Metrics Query
    User->>Proxy: GET /api/prometheus?query=...<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    Dashboard->>Prom: HTTPS/9091 Prometheus Query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Prom-->>Dashboard: Metrics Data (JSON)
    Dashboard-->>Proxy: HTTP Response
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS Metrics Response

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 4: WebSocket Event Stream
    User->>Proxy: WSS Upgrade Request<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Dashboard: WS/8080<br/>Bearer Token
    Dashboard->>K8s: Watch Notebook Events<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Dashboard: Event Stream (HTTPS)
    Dashboard-->>Proxy: WS Event Stream
    Proxy-->>User: WSS Event Stream (TLS)
